des:
Have questions about your CareSource plan? Find the health care answers you need, 24/7. The CareSource skill lets you access your member ID, learn more about your benefits, and much more!


A few things to try:
“Alexa, ask CareSource…”

• How do I find a doctor? 
• When is flu season?
• Are flu shots covered?
• How do I get a new ID card?
• What is a well-visit?
• How do I reach CareSource?

The information that you share with this skill can be viewed by others who use your Alexa devices. To protect your interactions with this skill, your Alexa activity will not be viewable in the Alexa App or at www.amazon.com/alexaprivacysettings. 

This skill is for informational use only. It should not replace medical advice you get from a doctor. Call 911 if you have an emergency.
